<h2 id="context">Context</h2>
<div class="article-section">
	Morses Club PLC was a UK consumer finance company that offered a variety of loan products including home collected credit and online lending. 
	At the time of this project, Morses were making a push to move the majority of their services to digital and improve the usability of their existing digital lending services.
</div>

